quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  30,11,"God originates creation in the first instance, and then reproduces it, (and will bring it back in the Hereafter), and then you will be returned to Him"
  30,12,"When the Last Hour stands forth and the Judgment is established, the disbelieving criminals will be plunged into despair"
  30,13,"They will have no intercessors in the beings whom they associate (as partners with God), and they will no longer believe in their being partners with God"
  30,14,When the Last Hour stands forth (and the Judgment is established) – on that Day all people will be separated from one another
  30,15,"As for those who believe and do good, righteous deeds, they will be honored and made happy in a delightful Garden"
  30,16,"But those who disbelieve and deny Our Revelations and the final meeting (with Us) in the Hereafter, such will be arraigned for punishment (in Hell)"
  30,17,So glorify God when you enter the evening and when you enter the morning
  30,18,– And (proclaim that) all praise and gratitude in the heavens and on the earth are for Him – and in the afternoon and when you enter the noon time
  30,19,"He brings forth the living out of the dead, and brings the dead out of the living, and revives the earth after its death. It is in the way (that He revives the dead earth that) you will be brought forth from the dead"